java.sql/RowIdLifetime/ROWID_VALID_OTHER.description:
Indicates that the lifetime of a RowId from this data source is indeterminate;
but not one of ROWID_VALID_TRANSACTION, ROWID_VALID_SESSION, or,
ROWID_VALID_FOREVER.

